title: How to Destroy Your Worrying
itunes:title: How to Destroy Your Worrying
description:
Episode 599 - Do you find yourself worrying too much? Do you get paralyzed because of how much you worry? Well in this episode I am going to teach you the simple strategy that I use to destroy my worries and take steps in the right direction in my life! If you are ready to break out of your comfort zones, join my Iron Mind 60 challenge at www.IronMind60.com
